favorites.content: There is no need for temples, no need for complicated philosophies. My brain and my heart are my temples; my philosophy is kindness.
favorites.author: Dalai Lama

favorites.content: Let me tell you the secret that has led me to my goal: my strength lies solely in my tenacity.
favorites.author: Louis Pasteur

quotes.content: Stay positive and happy. Work hard and don't give up hope.
quotes.author: Anonymous

quotes.content: Every day may not be good, but there is something good in every day.
quotes.author: Unknown

quotes.content: The only way to do great work is to love what you do.
quotes.author: Steve Jobs
